author: Alayna Treene
title: House passes historic $2 trillion coronavirus stimulus bill
description: The House passed the $2.2 trillion coronavirus stimulus bill on Friday via a voice vote. President Trump said he plans to sign the bill into law later today. Why it matters: What happens in Washington is often lost on the rest of the country. But this rescue …
content:
After days of intense negotiations, talks between Capitol Hill leaders and the White House over a Phase 3 stimulus package to fight the coronavirus broke down on Sunday, leading to a failed cloture vote meant to move the bill forward.
